description:
Bloody love Hardcore Henry? Just wait until you read the comic Hardcore Akan -- an origin story created by the film's director, Ilya Naishuller, Brian Phillipson and Will Stewart!

Before wreaking havoc in the film Hardcore Henry, our ruthless villain, Akan, wasn't always bad... Hardcore Akan uncovers what made him so potently evil; from his birth during the infamous Chernobyl disaster, to the discovery of his superpowers, to his ultimate rise as the head of Russia's most sinister robotics company.
Get an exclusive sneak-peek at Image Comics titles announced at Image Expo 2016, along with the first look at stunning preview pages you won't find elsewhere, from today's top comics industry talent.
